snippet.title: Christmas Run - Full Unedited Platinum Trophy Gameplay (PS4/PS5)
snippet.description:
#ChristmasRun #Gameplay #Platinum

- From @BreakSushi; this is my #Platinum #Trophy gameplay run from start to finish and can be used as a #TrophyGuide to obtain the #PlatinumTrophy.
#PS4 #PS4Share #PS5 #PS5Share #BreakSushi

The game can be purchased here for £6.49 -
https://store.playstation.com/en-gb/product/EP4312-PPSA06188_00-3112150176127444

Trophy List -
https://psnprofiles.com/trophies/15024-christmas-run/Dino_Roar

Trophy Guide available on @NODE_Gamers (https://nodegamers.com/) - 
https://nodegamers.com/2021/12/24/christmas-run-trophy-guide/

Description (From PSN Store) -
"ChristmasRun is a Runner style arcade game where the user leaps and dashes through obstacles to get to the finish line. Play and survive through 12 levels as Santa Claus to bring a Merry Christmas to all!"

Recorded Via:
Elgato HD60s - https://www.elgato.com/en/gaming/game-capture-hd60-s

Please Like & Subscribe if you like my content; it is appreciated more than you think.

Feel free to check out my other Social Networks: -
https://myurls.co/dino_roar

Instagram - @dino_roar - https://www.instagram.com/dino_roar/
PSN Profile - Dino_Roar - https://psnprofiles.com/Dino_Roar
Twitch - PSNDinoRoar -  https://m.twitch.tv/psndinoroar/profile
Twitter - @Dino_Roared - https://twitter.com/Dino_Roared
